data.text: Excellent. It seems the walls are no more.
Then let's get our asses in there!
Yeah, let's not waste any more—
Are you working hard to keep Sapporo clean?[0a]To make it a glistening, filth-free city?

Well, it's time for our regular cleanup! Anyone[0a]who calls themselves a proud member of my
staff must take initiative!

That means no slacking off, and not a single[0a]mote of dust left on the premises! I want this
place spotless!
Turn Sapporo into a paradise as pure as snow!
Bury them in pure, white snow! Heeee-HO!
What's up with these little freaks?
I can hardly believe my eyes!
They're chanting about some cleanup routine.[0a]Maybe this is a periodic security measure?

At any rate, it's too risky to charge in now.[0a]Let's head back to reality and see what
we can do.
Yeah. I don't see much point in staying here.
All right, good bit—now it's time to go.
